  Declaration
  <input type="checkbox" name="declaration" value="declared"> I declare under penalty of perjury, that the above information which I have set forth in this application is true and accurate to the best of my knowledge and that I agree to operate the above described business in strict compliance with city zoning regulations governing same.
</label>